      • transformToRdf

        public org.apache.jena.rdf.model.Model transformToRdf(DomainProfile profile)
                                               throws RDFTransformException
        Transforms a DomainProfile into a Jena RDF Model. The profile will be a blank node.
        Parameters:
        profile - The DomainProfile to transform.
        Returns:
        The Jena model containing the RDF representation of the DomainProfile
        Throws:
        RDFTransformException - if an error is encountered performing the transformation

      • transformToRdf

        public org.apache.jena.rdf.model.Model transformToRdf(DomainProfile profile,
                                                      String profileResourceURI)
                                               throws RDFTransformException
        Transforms a DomainProfile into a Jena RDF Model
        Parameters:
        profile - The DomainProfile to transform.
        profileResourceURI - If defined, the Profile resource will have this URI. If null, it will be a blank node.
        Returns:
        The Jena model containing the RDF representation of the DomainProfile
        Throws:
        RDFTransformException - if an error is encountered performing the transformation

      • transformToProfile

        public DomainProfile transformToProfile(org.apache.jena.rdf.model.Model model)

        Transforms a Jena model representing a DomainProfile in RDF into a DomainProfile object.
        Parameters:
        model - The model containing the DomainProfile
        Returns:
        The DomainProfile object that corresponds to the RDF
        Throws:
        RDFTransformException - if an error is encountered performing the transformation
